-   **ggplot3**: [Leaflet: An Introduction to Geographic Data Visualization](https://math3570-s24.github.io/website/documents/proposal_ggplot3.pdf)

-   **Win Rs**: [How You Can Sleep Better: A Data Analysis](https://math3570-s24.github.io/website/documents/proposal_WinR.pdf)

-   **Red Pandas**: [RGL: 3D Visualization of Trails](https://math3570-s24.github.io/website/documents/proposal_RedPandas.pdf)

-   **Big Meta Watchers**: [How to Use Data Science in Real-Life](https://math3570-s24.github.io/website/documents/proposal_bigmeta.pdf)

-   **Ctrl + Alt + Elite**: [Do you Believe in Magick?](https://math3570-s24.github.io/website/documents/proposal_CtrlAltDelete.pdf)

-   **GitClub**: [Web Development: Utilizing Quarto to Creat a Website](https://math3570-s24.github.io/website/documents/proposal_GitClub.pdf)

-   **Data Dawgs**: [Datadawgs Take on College](https://math3570-s24.github.io/website/documents/proposal_datadawg.pdf)

## Final Project

- **14 - 15 min** presentation
- You evaluate **all group projects except the one you work on** based on
  + Project Content and Organization (8 pts)
  + Presentation Material (Slides) Quality (4 pts)
  + Oral Presentation Skill and Delivery (4 pts)
  + Interactions and Q&A (4 pts)
- You choose **one single** person who you think contributes the most to your group project.

